source.name: Retail Food Stores Map
source.description: The point map shows the locations of all retail food stores which are licensed by the Department of Agriculture and Markets. The initial view of the map is broken up into large geographic areas and displays the number of retail food stores in each area. To drill down to a smaller geographic area, click directly on the area of the map or click the plus sign to zoom in on the map.  Data is the most recently submitted and available data. This map is currently a snapshot in time. For more information check out http://www.agriculture.ny.gov/FS/FSHome.html, or go to the "About" section.
